Running slirp4netns with `--mtu=65520` significantly improves the throughtput ([1.07 Gbps -> 9.21 Gbps](https://github.com/rootless-containers/slirp4netns/tree/777bdccceffa5bee38dbfd9eefc06628cc160ff6#iperf3-netns---host )) .

I also would like to hear performance & stability feedback about `--mtu=65520` from Podman community.

